metadata.title: Quadrangle Boundaries 1:63,360 - DNR

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources, Division of Support Services-Land Records Information Section

metadata.description: Data Type: Base Maps  ;This coverage contains the boundaries of the USGS protracted 1:63,360 quadrangle maps covering Alaska. DNR converted corner coordinates from BLM, AEH files into ARC/INFO coverages. The unique tic numbering system allows future development of statewide digital libraries using these boundaries as reference tiles.
